    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x6s0w59hrsoc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 995,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "③  What actually crosses each wire (with sample payloads)",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xr0hq4sd962",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1035,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "text": "Boundary ①  Claude  ↔  qz-mcp-server",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x9s1hqb8us0w",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1058,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Format: JSON-RPC 2.0 over HTTP POST to /mcp.  Carrier: text only.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x9lcz6a5xxl6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1080,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Example tool call (Claude → server):",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xu2z5s7mys",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1100,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "text": "{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\", \"id\":42, \"method\":\"tools/call\",",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xgdutzlvsusg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1115,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "text": " \"params\":{\"name\":\"speak\", \"arguments\":{\"text\":\"Hi, please introduce yourself.\"}}}",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x4mva7v2bpqw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1140,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Server response:",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xafqmupv5hz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1160,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "text": "{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\", \"id\":42,",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xj8y6a3cfais",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1175,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "text": " \"result\":{\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"true\"}], \"isError\":false}}",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x6wezb2cqjy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1035,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "text": "Boundary ②  qz-mcp-server  ↔  Pipecat child",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x9ykzr0myrtb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1058,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Format: Python dicts pickled across multiprocessing.Queue.  In-host only.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xd7pjshlzhpw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1080,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Example command (parent → child):",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xmgiixkbmthc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 1100,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "text": "{\"cmd\": \"listen\", \"timeout\": 60.0}",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xyd70hgo70x",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1125,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Example response (child → parent):",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xcvjbswcqkuk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 1145,
      "strokeColor": "#e67700",
      "text": "{\"text\": \"Linear is a project management tool ...\"}",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x6ligh9zyr4h",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1170,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Why a separate process?  Pipecat owns its own asyncio loop and audio threads.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xczw35u4wn7m",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 1185,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Running it inline would block FastMCP's HTTP server.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xsch303l94f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1225,
      "strokeColor": "#5f3dc4",
      "text": "Boundary ③  Pipecat child  ↔  Daily room  ↔  Toocan bot",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x7bqt8znmfwo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1248,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Format: WebRTC SRTP audio frames + JSON \"app messages\" on the data-channel.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xipas2q8kvl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1268,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "Audio is what makes the actual conversation work.  Data-channel = sideband signalling.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x4eaawplhft9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1293,
      "strokeColor": "#5f3dc4",
      "text": "Audio path — our pipeline OUT: KokoroTTS → PCM frames → transport.output() → Daily → Toocan bot's STT",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x6y8uiw5ye53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1308,
      "strokeColor": "#5f3dc4",
      "text": "Audio path — our pipeline IN:  Toocan bot's TTS → Daily → transport.input() → Whisper-MLX → listen() return value",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xfmrn2bjhizs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1335,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "text": "Data-channel — RTVI app messages (we DISABLED these on our side):",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xb8mngzhj41e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 1352,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "text": "{\"label\":\"rtvi-ai\", \"type\":\"bot-tts-started\", \"id\":\"...\", \"data\":{...}}",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xzelvi1nsb6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1372,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "text": "Useful only if a browser SDK is at one end rendering UI.  In our headless setup they're noise + a",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xrh8wpcqgtos",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1387,
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "text": "validation-error feedback loop (RTVIMessage schema requires `id`, server-events ship without it).",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xz1pz1ms65o7",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1430,
      "width": 1320,
      "height": 260,
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "strokeColor": "#adb5bd",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x4geoi2zr5zk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1445,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "④  End-to-end sequence: a single conversation turn",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xledxsneajjn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1480,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "1. Claude → server:  tools/call name=\"speak\" arguments={\"text\":\"Hi, please introduce yourself.\"}",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xwz4cj86d42",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1502,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "2. server → child:   {\"cmd\":\"speak\", \"text\":\"Hi, please introduce yourself.\"}",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xy93rrk89j5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1524,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "3. child:  KokoroTTS synthesises PCM → DailyTransport.output() pushes opus frames into the room.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xc6lxe0ki9m",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1546,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "4. Toocan bot:  receives audio → ElevenLabs STT → Anthropic LLM → ElevenLabs TTS → pushes audio back.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xahi46zyig3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1568,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "5. child:  DailyTransport.input() receives audio → Whisper-MLX transcribes → SmartTurn marks end-of-turn.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xx1kvfo9g65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1590,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "text": "6. server → Claude:  tools/call name=\"listen\" returns {\"text\":\"Hi there. I'm an onboarding assistant ...\"}",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46xxa2uxcz01a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1615,
      "strokeColor": "#555",
      "text": "Total wall-clock time we measured per turn: ~10–15 s, dominated by the bot's LLM + TTS, not by our pipeline.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mpdlf46x7tx2izjcjd3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1645,
      "strokeColor": "#868e96",
      "text": "(TODO: drop in your own observations about latency, failure modes, what you'd change about the contract.)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-20T05:00:06.034Z",
      "version": 1
    }
  ],
  "appState": {
    "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff",
    "gridSize": null
  }
}